</div>
			<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en">Bernard–Soulier syndrome</h1>
									<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
									<div id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</div>
								<div id="contentSub"><span class="mw-redirectedfrom">  (Redirected from <a href="/w/index.php?title=Hemorrhagiparous_thrombocytic_dystrophy&amp;redirect=no" title="Hemorrhagiparous thrombocytic dystrophy">Hemorrhagiparous thrombocytic dystrophy</a>)</span></div>
												<div id="jump-to-nav" class="mw-jump">
